      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I can provide you with a basic automated test suite in Cypress that covers the main user flow. This suite will include tests for login, dashboard, and profile update, and it will use a combination of mocking and retries to handle the flaky auth service.\n\n```javascript\n// cypress/integration/user-flow.spec.js\n\ndescribe('User Flow', () => {\n  beforeEach(() => {\n    // Mock auth service to return a valid token\n    cy.intercept('POST', '/auth/login', {\n      statusCode: 200,\n      body: {\n        token: 'valid-token',\n      },\n    });\n  });\n\n  it('should login successfully', () => {\n    // Login with valid credentials\n    cy.visit('/login');\n    cy.get('input[name=\"username\"]').type('valid-username');\n    cy.get('input[name=\"password\"]').type('valid-password');\n    cy.get('button[type=\"submit\"]').click();\n\n    // Wait for the auth service to return a token\n    cy.wait(1000);\n\n    // Verify the token is valid\n    cy.intercept('GET', '/auth/me', {\n      statusCode: 200,\n      body: {\n        token: 'valid-token',\n      },\n    }).as('me');",
